        "stdout": "The argument 'SmtpServer' is required if the following argument(s) are not specified: Help\r\n\r\nPick your secret santa without needing everyone in the office\r\n\r\nUsage - SecretSanta -options\r\n\r\nGlobalOption        Description\nHelp (-h)           Displays the help information\nSmtpServer (-s)     The address of the SMTP server with optional port (e.g.\n                    smtp.mailtrap.io:465), default port is 465\nSmtpUsername (-u)   User for the SMTP server\nSmtpPassword (-p)   Password for the SMTP server\nFromAddress (-f)    The email address of the sender\nInputPath (-i)      Path to the input CSV file containing participants and\n                    their email addresses\nMessagePath (-m)    Path to the message HTML file",
